Jennifer O'Neill https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jennifer_O%27Neill 0 Jennifer O'Neill (born February 20, 1948) is a Brazilian American actress, model, author and speaker, known for her role in the 1971 film Summer of '42 and modelling for CoverGirl cosmetics starting in the 1970s.
